Reserved: application-layer (use-case) sources for the consensus context.
The orphan demo use case application_consensus_validate_block was removed
(Law 8 — subtraction before addition; zero production callers). This
directory is kept as the documented hexagonal "application layer" scaffold
(see Makefile APPLICATION_CONTEXTS) so the next real use case has a home —
there is no other home for a future consensus use-case to go. (Contrast
app/events/, a similar reserved-empty placeholder that WAS deleted
2026-07-17: its concept already had a real home elsewhere, lib/event/ +
lib/storage/event_log.c, so the empty placeholder was pure cruft. See
docs/FRAMEWORK.md §3 row 7.)
